I"<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>free | grep Mem | awk '{ printf("mem free: %.0f%\n", $4/($3+$4) * 100.0) }
# returns
# mem free: 30%
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>With perc2 script</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>perc2 $(free | grep Mem | awk '{ printf("%.0f\n", $4/($3+$4) * 100.0) }') 100
# returns
# █████████████████████████████████████████████
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>in tint2, executor, numeral</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>#-------------------------------------
# Executor Mem
execp = new
execp_command = free | grep Mem | awk '{ printf("%.0f% mem free\n", $4/($3+$4) * 100.0) }'
execp_interval = 5
execp_has_icon = 0
execp_cache_icon = 0
execp_continuous = 0
execp_tooltip = mem free in percents
execp_padding = 0 0
execp_font = cuprum 12
execp_font_color = #111111 40
</code></pre></div></div>

